{"word":"Brother","slug":"brother","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Brother</b> Signifies a:<br/> - Relative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=16'>Gen 14:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=29&verse=12'>Gen 29:12</a> <br/> - Neighbor<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=7'>Deu 23:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=21&verse=6'>Jdg 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=5&verse=7'>Neh 5:7</a> <br/> - Any Israelite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=34&verse=9'>Jer 34:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=10'>Oba 1:10</a> <br/> - Mankind<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=5'>Gen 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=35'>Mat 18:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=15'>1Jn 3:15</a> <br/> - Companion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=26'>2Sa 1:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=13&verse=30'>1Ki 13:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=33'>1Ki 20:33</a> <br/> Love of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=17&verse=17'>Pro 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=18&verse=24'>Pro 18:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=8&verse=1'>Son 8:1</a><br/> Unfaithful<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=27&verse=10'>Pro 27:10</a><br/> Reuben's love for Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=22'>Gen 37:22</a><br/> Joseph's for his brethren<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=43&verse=34'>Gen 43:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=45&verse=5'>Gen 45:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=25'>Gen 50:25</a><br/> A fraternal epithet, especially among Christians<br/> - Instituted by Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=50'>Mat 12:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=25&verse=40'>Mat 25:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=12'>Heb 2:12</a> <br/> - Used by disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=17'>Act 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=20'>Act 21:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=16&verse=23'>Rom 16:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=12'>1Co 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=2&verse=13'>2Co 2:13</a> <br/> - Used by Peter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=22'>1Pe 1:22</a> <br/> - Used among the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=17'>Lev 19:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=4'>Deu 22:4</a> <br/> Brother's widow, law concerning Levirate marriage of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=10'>Deu 25:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=24'>Mat 22:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=12&verse=19'>Mar 12:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=20&verse=28'>Luk 20:28</a>"}]}